{"type":null,"faqId":12921,"title":"P7 通话声音很小或有杂音，如何解决","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>通话过程中按音量上键可以提高通话音量。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请在网络信号较好和噪音干扰小的环境下通话。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>将耳朵对准听筒的位置，可有效提高通话音量。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请不要用手指或其他物体遮挡住麦克风（通常在手机底部），声源不要远离麦克风。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请使用华为标配耳机进行通话，非标配耳机可能会出现不兼容的情况。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若问题依然存在，请重启手机或备份重要数据后恢复出厂设置。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若重启手机或恢复出厂设置后通话仍然有问题，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=35379\" /> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">进入</span> <span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/service-center/index.htm\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/service-center/index.htm</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">查询全国服务网点；</span> <span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">或关注华为终端官方微信平台：华为终端（微信号：</span><span>huaweizhongduan</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">），点击“自助服务</span><span> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">服务中心查询”根据屏幕提示查询最近的服务网点。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">华为会在官网发布最新软件版本，请前往</span><span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">根据型号查询；或通过在线升级进行手机软件版本更新，以获得更好的使用体验。</span></span> \n</p>"